query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `generated_reports` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `projectId` int NOT NULL,
  `templateId` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `reportName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `reportType` enum('executive_summary','detailed_assessment','financial_analysis','compliance','risk_assessment','optimization_results','custom') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'custom',
  `status` enum('draft','finalized','archived') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'draft',
  `generatedBy` int NOT NULL,
  `pdfUrl` text,
  `docxUrl` text,
  `xlsxUrl` text,
  `metadata` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_report_project` (`projectId`),
  KEY `idx_report_template` (`templateId`),
  KEY `idx_report_generated_by` (`generatedBy`),
  KEY `idx_report_status` (`status`)
)
